FW Reliant RFP Price to BeatOriginal Message From Curry Mike Sent Wednesday August PM To Trefz Greg Compean Karla Subject FW Reliant RFP Price to Beat Im putting this on your list Let me know who wants to work this one Due sep th Original Message From avigantconsultingcom mailto avigantconsultingcom Sent Friday August PM Subject Reliant RFP The following email was sent earlier today regarding the Reliant RFP for of its Price to Beat load We received your email back due to the size of the file We have reconfigured appendix b and attached it below as special appendix b so that the size of the file would be smaller and go through your firewall The information contained in special appendix b is the same as appendix b the original sent If you have any questions or problems with the following please call me at Thanks for your patience Nicole Brady Attached is an electronic copy of the Reliant Energy Services Request for Proposal for Power Supply to of its Price to Beat Load A hard copy of this RFP has also been forwarded via FedEx for delivery to your attention today The FedEx package also includes a CD with the detail load profile information A typical transmittal letter is attached providing an overview of the supply requirements planned RFP administration and proposal requirements Proposals are due on September A preproposal meeting will be held August at the Reliant Energy Plaza in Houston TX RSVP is required as lunch will be provided Your review and consideration of this RFP is appreciated see attached file RFPcoverletterdoc FinalRFPdoc AppendixAdoc AppendixBdoc Sincerely Nicole Brady Navigant Consulting Inc See attached file RFP cover letterdocSee attached file Final RFPdoc See attached file Appendix AdocSee attached file special appendix bdoc
